statements: SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorTracking;
SELECT quantum_circuit_id, error_type FROM QuantumErrorTracking;
SELECT error_type, correction_strategy FROM QuantumErrorTracking ORDER BY quantum_circuit_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorTracking WHERE error_type = 'X';
SELECT DISTINCT error_type FROM QuantumErrorTracking;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorTracking WHERE quantum_circuit_id = 1;
SELECT error_type, correction_strategy FROM QuantumErrorTracking WHERE quantum_circuit_id = 1;
SELECT DISTINCT error_type FROM QuantumErrorTracking;
SELECT quantum_circuit_id, error_type, correction_strategy FROM QuantumErrorTracking ORDER BY quantum_circuit_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumErrorTracking WHERE error_type LIKE '%Qubit%';
SELECT error_description, error_name FROM ErrorTypes;
SELECT * FROM CorrectionStrategies;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM CorrectionStrategies WHERE strategy_id = 3;
SELECT error_name, error_description FROM ErrorTypes WHERE error_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT error_name, error_description FROM ErrorTypes ORDER BY error_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM ErrorTypes WHERE error_id > 5;
SELECT error_name, error_description FROM ErrorTypes WHERE error_description LIKE '%error%';
SELECT * FROM ErrorTypes ORDER BY error_name DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, COUNT(*) as total_strategies FROM CorrectionStrategies GROUP BY strategy_name HAVING total_strategies > 1;
SELECT error_name, strategy_name FROM ErrorTypes JOIN CorrectionStrategies ON ErrorTypes.error_id = CorrectionStrategies.strategy_id;
SELECT * FROM Errors;
SELECT error_id, error_type FROM Errors ORDER BY error_id DESC;
SELECT error_type, error_description FROM Errors WHERE error_type='server';
SELECT * FROM CorrectionStrategies WHERE strategy_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_details FROM CorrectionStrategies ORDER BY strategy_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Errors ORDER BY error_id DESC;
SELECT error_type, error_description FROM Errors WHERE error_type LIKE 'Database%';
SELECT e.error_id, e.error_type, c.strategy_name FROM Errors e JOIN ErrorCorrectionMapping m ON e.error_id = m.error_id JOIN CorrectionStrategies c ON m.strategy_id = c.strategy_id;
SELECT DISTINCT e.error_type FROM Errors e JOIN ErrorCorrectionMapping m ON e.error_id = m.error_id WHERE m.strategy_id = 2;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_errors, AVG(error_id) AS avg_error_id FROM Errors;
SELECT * FROM Errors;
SELECT error_id, error_type FROM Errors WHERE error_type = 'Database';
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM Correction_Strategies ORDER BY strategy_name DESC;
SELECT error_id, error_description, error_type FROM Errors WHERE error_id > 5;
SELECT * FROM Circuit_Errors WHERE circuit_name LIKE '%ABC%' ORDER BY error_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM Errors;
SELECT error_id, error_type FROM Errors WHERE error_type = 'Database';
SELECT * FROM Errors ORDER BY error_type DESC;

SELECT Errors.error_id, Errors.error_type, Correction_Strategies.strategy_name FROM Errors INNER JOIN Error_Corrections ON Errors.error_id = Error_Corrections.error_id INNER JOIN Correction_Strategies ON Error_Corrections.strategy_id = Correction_Strategies.strategy_id;

SELECT Circuit_Errors.circuit_name, Errors.error_type, Correction_Strategies.strategy_name FROM Circuit_Errors INNER JOIN Errors ON Circuit_Errors.error_id = Errors.error_id INNER JOIN Error_Corrections ON Errors.error_id = Error_Corrections.error_id INNER JOIN Correction_Strategies ON Error_Corrections.strategy_id = Correction_Strategies.strategy_id ORDER BY Circuit_Errors.circuit_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM ErrorTypes;
SELECT error_id, error_name FROM ErrorTypes WHERE error_id = 1;
SELECT circuit_name, error_id, strategy_id FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE strategy_id IS NOT NULL;
SELECT log_id, log_message FROM ErrorLogs ORDER BY log_id DESC;
SELECT circuit_name, circuit_id, error_id, strategy_id FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE error_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM ErrorTypes;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_id FROM CorrectionStrategies ORDER BY strategy_name DESC;
SELECT circuit_name, error_id, strategy_id FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE circuit_id = 5;
SELECT log_message FROM ErrorLogs WHERE log_id = 3;

SELECT CircuitErrors.circuit_error_id, CircuitErrors.timestamp, QuantumCircuits.circuit_name, ErrorTypes.error_name FROM CircuitErrors JOIN QuantumCircuits ON CircuitErrors.circuit_id = QuantumCircuits.circuit_id JOIN ErrorTypes ON CircuitErrors.error_id = ErrorTypes.error_id WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
